    "In C/S mode, a new database service process (gserver) is generated to handle user requests.",
    "In D/A mode, applications directly access the database without a separate service process.",
    "The SUNDB cluster system ensures ACID compliance for transactions executed in the cluster.",
    "Each database in the SUNDB cluster system has a similar architecture to the standalone version with added processes for cluster communication."
